text: Kaal Bhairav Rahasya (season 2) is an Indian television soap opera thriller series. The series will be produced by Ravi Garahni and directed by Dharmesh Shah. It premiered in 2018, broadcast on Star Bharat. It stars Gautam Rode and Additi Gupta in the lead roles. ==Cast== * Gautam Rode * Additi Gupta * ==References== Category:2017 Indian television series debuts Category:Mystery television series Category:Hindi-language television series
